“Every vehicle in our Houston-area fleet is equipped with wide area two-way radio service provided by pdvWIRELESS. The clarity on our two-way radios operating on the pdvWIRELESS system is outstanding and it’s added an extra layer of security for our students.”
Gold Star Transit, Houston, Kirk Wilkie, Vice President Read More


