Dealers



pdvWireless has several unique opportunities to add value to your dealer organization and network of customers through our new robust workforce management solution, DispatchPlus. Once the network build-out is complete, pdvWireless will own the only national wireless network that is exclusively dedicated to serving dispatch-centric enterprises.
For more information on becoming a DispatchPlus dealer, just fill out and submit the request form below.  A leader from our DispatchPlus Dealer team will contact you.

