pdvWireless is a national wireless provider that delivers proven commercial push-to-talk solutions that help our customers more effectively solve their mobile communications challenges.








pdvWireless is a national wireless provider that delivers proven commercial push-to-talk solutions that help our customers more effectively solve their mobile communications challenges.








pdvWireless is a national wireless provider that delivers proven commercial push-to-talk solutions that help our customers more effectively solve their mobile communications challenges.








pdvWireless is a national wireless provider that delivers proven commercial push-to-talk solutions that help our customers more effectively solve their mobile communications challenges.









pdvWireless is a recognized leader in mobile workforce communications and location-based solutions. We help organizations increase the productivity of field-based workers and the efficiency of their dispatch and call center operations.
With our nationwide 900 MHz spectrum licenses, pdvWireless is transforming the wireless communications space with the largest, private push-to-talk, two-way radio network that is dedicated to serving dispatch-oriented businesses across major U.S. markets. Our revolutionary new DispatchPlus is designed to significantly enhance field-to-office communications through patented radio technology and proprietary cloud-based mobile workforce applications.

While DispatchPlus represents the next step in the evolution of pdvWireless, the company continues to support its robust workforce management application pdvConnect through valued carrier partners.
By focusing on industry verticals with highly mobile workforces, such as transportation, distribution, construction, security, hospitality, waste management and field services, pdvWireless is filling a critical gap in the telecommunications marketplace. Our technology helps companies communicate faster and more efficiently and connect large groups more seamlessly. The power of push-to-talk technology and our superior network coverage provide greater productivity and enhanced responsiveness.





 
 

 

 
