pdvWireless, Inc. Key Developments

pdvWireless, Inc. Presents at Citi's 2017 Small & Mid Cap Conference, Jun-08-2017 10:15 AM
Jun 7 17
pdvWireless, Inc. Presents at Citi's 2017 Small & Mid Cap Conference, Jun-08-2017 10:15 AM. Venue: The Plaza Hotel, New York, New York, United States. Speakers: John C. Pescatore, Chief Executive Officer, President and Director, Morgan E. O'Brien, Vice Chairman.


pdvWireless, Inc. Reports Unaudited Consolidated Financial Results for the Fourth Quarter and Full Year Ended March 31, 2017
Jun 6 17
pdvWireless, Inc. reported unaudited consolidated financial results for the fourth quarter and full year ended March 31, 2017. For the quarter, total operating revenues were $1,264,000 against $951,000 for the same period of last year. Loss from operations was $7,554,000 against $6,796,000 for the same period of last year. Loss before income taxes was $7,515,000 against $6,774,000 for the same period of last year. Net loss was $14,014,000 against $6,774,000 for the same period of last year. Net loss per basic and diluted share was $0.97 against $0.47 for the same period of last year. Adjusted EBITDA was $5,830,000 against $5,145,000 for the same period of last year.

For the year, total operating revenues were $4,787,000 against $3,544,000 for the same period of last year. Loss from operations was $32,783,000 against $21,930,000 for the same period of last year. Loss before income taxes was $732,688,000 against $21,828,000 for the same period of last year. Net loss was $39,186,000 against $21,828,000 for the same period of last year. Net loss per basic and diluted share was $2.72 against $1.54 for the same period of last year. Adjusted EBITDA was $25,795,000 against $16,404,000 for the same period of last year. Net cash used in operating activities was $26,647,000 against $19,794,000 for the same period of last year. Purchases of intangible assets was $750,000 against $2,068,000 for the same period of last year. Purchases of equipment was $1,640,000 against $9,077,000 for the same period of last year. Payments for patent costs was $1,000 against $12,000 for the same period of last year.


pdvWireless, Inc. to Report Q4, 2017 Results on Jun 06, 2017
Jun 2 17
pdvWireless, Inc. announced that they will report Q4, 2017 results at 5:00 PM, Eastern Standard Time on Jun 06, 2017


